  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of ghee in a cataplana over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, cumin, turmeric, and paprika and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chickpeas, pickled jalape\u001510, and demerara sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot."
